{"tid":45331,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"傳奇一生九段婚姻，艷星莎莎嘉寶因心臟病發辭世，享年九十九歲","createTime":"2016-12-19T02:06:11.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-19T02:59:56.000Z","uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e73f7d5f33d142056a64073dece5216279864ada","tid":45331,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T02:06:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://classiccinemaphotos.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/Zsa-Zsa-Gabor-looking-sexy-in-fishnet-stockings-and-zebra-print-ca.-1950s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fclassiccinemaphotos.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F09%2FZsa-Zsa-Gabor-looking-sexy-in-fishnet-stockings-and-zebra-print-ca.-1950s.jpg&h=e4688337&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/.a/6a00d8341c630a53ef0147e2fef769970b-400wi\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Flatimesblogs.latimes.com%2F.a%2F6a00d8341c630a53ef0147e2fef769970b-400wi&h=db7137ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img5.cna.com.tw/www/WebPhotos/800/20161219/39621977.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg5.cna.com.tw%2Fwww%2FWebPhotos%2F800%2F20161219%2F39621977.jpg&h=52709db8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好萊塢老牌女星莎莎嘉寶（圖）的丈夫表示，莎莎嘉寶18日心臟病發作辭世，享壽99歲。（圖取自維基共享資源；圖版權屬公眾領域）<br />\n<br />\n（中央社洛杉磯18日綜合外電報導）好萊塢老牌女星莎莎嘉寶（Zsa Zsa Gabor）的丈夫表示，出生匈牙利、戀愛經歷或許比銀幕成績還耀眼的莎莎嘉寶今天心臟病發作辭世，享壽99歲。<br />\n<br />\n法新社報導，莎莎嘉寶的夫婿馮安沃（Frederic von Anhalt）接受法新社電訪時，情緒激動地表示，莎莎嘉寶在朋友與家人陪伴下逝世，「每個人都在那，她不是孤獨終老。」<br />\n<br />\n根據電影網站IMDb，莎莎嘉寶曾主演「紅磨坊」（Moulin Rouge）、「莉莉」（Lili）及「歷劫佳人」（Touch of Evil）等電影。<br />\n<br />\n莎莎嘉寶出生於匈牙利，一生結過9次婚，並稱呼每個人「親愛的」（Darling）。（譯者：中央社周莉芳）1051219<br />\n<br />\n轉自中央通訊社<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201612195003-1.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F201612195003-1.aspx&d=rrT9AL%2Fi%2FwiN14iGQi62JZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=a141bed5\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201612195003-1.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"947d8364331a52d83aa1d2ec6aaebf9f8cb4829d","tid":45331,"uid":18320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T02:07:54.000Z","msg":"屌你老母留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51743bc565eb2d9e2f72d656086d846bb9306708","tid":45331,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T02:28:49.000Z","msg":"雞"},{"pid":"74ae136bbdb2d6e1aa13a1c489ab97ec2b9fb48c","tid":45331,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T02:59:56.000Z","msg":"公廁"}]}